  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dark Hours</strong> is a co-op survival horror game for up to 4 players.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You and your crew were ready for the perfect heist, until something went terribly wrong. Right after breaking in, the power cuts out and you realize something isn’t right. You’re trapped inside the building you came to rob… and you’re not alone. A monster has taken over the place and you’re its next prey. Will you manage to escape? Will you survive this apocalyptic night? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/8f2e9e2f1d3acb6d21d6ea2d70183c2b.poster.avif?t=1773832118\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/8f2e9e2f1d3acb6d21d6ea2d70183c2b.webm?t=1773832118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/8f2e9e2f1d3acb6d21d6ea2d70183c2b.mp4?t=1773832118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAN. BREAK. STEAL.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Alone or with friends: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore <strong>5 environments</strong>: an auction house, a museum, a casino, a power plant and a cruise ship</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong>Use <strong>50+ heist items</strong>: hacking tools, EMPs, scanners, cameras, teleporters, tasers and more. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Complete <strong>12+ mission objectives</strong>: steal precious artifacts, destroy evidence, blow up the building, escape with the jackpot and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Steal valuable loot</strong>, complete your contracts, and score big!  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/1097280a4b6fa8242cba97e2937de663.poster.avif?t=1773832118\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/1097280a4b6fa8242cba97e2937de663.webm?t=1773832118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/1097280a4b6fa8242cba97e2937de663.mp4?t=1773832118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COOPERATE. SURVIVE. ESCAPE.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>8 unique monsters</strong>, each with their own abilities, strengths and weaknesses. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dynamic <strong>co-op gameplay</strong>: solve puzzles and minigames, deactivate lasers and security cameras, share (or steal) the loot. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be stealthy</strong> and aware of your surroundings: every bad step can attract the monsters. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive together</strong>… or <strong>use your friends</strong> to get out alive.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/da50ad2b132214d2fd79568fd9e2f51e.poster.avif?t=1773832118\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/da50ad2b132214d2fd79568fd9e2f51e.webm?t=1773832118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/da50ad2b132214d2fd79568fd9e2f51e.mp4?t=1773832118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY. EARN. REPEAT.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>3 mafia factions</strong> to build your reputation and unlock rare, useful, and fun gear among 50+ items. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100+ customization</strong> items to define your own style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>4 difficulty levels</strong>, including a Nightmare Mode. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/2cd3c9e558c1d2d8acbfac73841d913a.poster.avif?t=1773832118\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/2cd3c9e558c1d2d8acbfac73841d913a.webm?t=1773832118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208570/extras/2cd3c9e558c1d2d8acbfac73841d913a.mp4?t=1773832118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Warning: </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game contains flashing lights that may make it unsuitable for people with photosensitive epilepsy or other photosensitive conditions. Player discretion is advised.</p>",
